      "updated": 1782304017841,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Fonctions anonymes (lambda)\n\n    || 4                   () => 4\n    |x| x + 4             (x) => x + 4\n    |x: u16| x + 4\n    |x, y| x + y + 3     (x, y) => x + y + 3\n\n    let y = 5;\n\n    |x| x + y + 3",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Fonctions anonymes (lambda)\n\n    || 4                   () => 4\n    |x| x + 4             (x) => x + 4\n    |x: u16| x + 4\n    |x, y| x + y + 3     (x, y) => x + y + 3\n\n    let y = 5;\n\n    |x| x + y + 3",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
